{"comments":"Typography Token molecule.\n\nA TypeToken binds a semantic name to a typography style definition.\nTypography tokens define consistent text styles across the design system.\n\n## Structure\n\n```\nTypeToken = TokenMeta + TypeStyle\n```\n\n## Type Scale\n\nStandard semantic names for typography:\n- `type.display` — Large hero text\n- `type.h1` through `type.h6` — Heading hierarchy\n- `type.body.lg` / `type.body.md` / `type.body.sm` — Body text\n- `type.caption` — Small supporting text\n- `type.overline` — Label/category text\n- `type.code` — Monospace code text\n\n## At Billion-Agent Scale\n\nTypography creates visual hierarchy. When agents use semantic\ntype tokens, the reading experience remains consistent across\nall generated content.\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Typography design token.\n\nBinds a semantic name to a type style with role metadata.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["meta",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token"],"TokenMeta"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["style",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token","Type"],"TypeStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["role",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token","Type"],"TypeRole"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[357,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Token/Type.purs","start":[353,1]},"title":"TypeToken"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a type token with full metadata.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[